<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>مَنْ نُسِبَ إِلَى غَيْرِ أَبِيهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٣٢ - وَادْرِ الَّذِي لِغَيْرِ أَبٍّ يَنْتَسِبْ … خَوْفَ تَعَدُّدٍ إِذَا لَهُ نُسِبْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٣٣ - كَابْنِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَمَامَةٍ»</span> لِأُمٍّ، وَابْنِ … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُنْيَةَ»</span> جَدَّةٍ، وَلِلتَّبَنِّي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٩٣٤ - مِقْدَادٌ ابْنُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْأَسْوَدِ»</span>، ابْنُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«جَارِيَهْ»</span> … جَدٍّ، وَفِي ذَلِكَ كُتْبٌ وَافِيَهْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>• • •<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>